What is the best way to study ? This is a very important question. Some
 Chinese students often   1    very hard   2    long hours. This is a 
 3    habit (习惯), but it is not a better way to study . A good student
 must   4    enough sleep, enough food and enough rest. Every   5    
 you    6    to take a walk or play basketball or ping-pong or sing a
