 better. A nurse will come __3__ give you the first one this evening, and 
 then you’ll __4__ get another one tomorrow evening.” __5__ a young nurse 
 came to Mr. Green’s bed and said to him, “I am going to give you your __6__ 
 injection now, Mr. Green. Where do you want it?”
The old man was __7__. He looked at the nurse for a __8__, then he said,
 “__9__ has ever let me choose that before. Are you really going to let me choose now?”
“Yes, Mr. Green,” the nurse answered. She was in a hurry. “Where do you want it?”
“Well, then,” the old man answered __10__ “I want it in your left arm, please.”
